title: DPS-BEST OF- Sep 28, 2020

description:
On Today's episode of the DP Show, Dan wraps up all the action that went down around the NFL in Week 3. Have we seen the last of Mitchell Trubisky in Chicago? What's the biggest difference between this Seahawks teams and their Super Bowl contending teams from years past? We're joined by Former NFL lineman/Westwood One Analyst Ross Tucker and NBA HOF Reggie Miller. Plus the back row was out in observance of Yom Kipuur, but McLovin couldn't help but call in to talk Eagles football.
